   <h1>The Troll&#39;s Bane Chronicle</h1>

   <h2>The fifth year of the new era: May</h2>

<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 1st, Moathia invites everyone to a dance competition. Winner of the single dance is Sharmayne. Winners of the couple dance are Stephen and Josefine. </p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 1st, the orc clan "Wolves of Moshran" resigns under the leadership of Lorck.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 2nd, Pendar invites all to a meeting of the town guard. New recruits could join there.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 2nd, Salathe complains about two dwarves, one of them named Flint. Who threathened him in Silverbrand. Galim points out that they aren't citizens of Silverbrand.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 6th, the town guard warns of the murderous halfing Ziel. One day after he gets banned from town, he is attacked and killed while trying to enter.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 10th, Lord Aristeaus of the North beckons his people to renew the land of Varshikar.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 10th, King Tialdin invites all dwarves for a dwarven meeting on May 13th.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 11th, Misjbar publishes a collection of poems.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 12th, someone kidnaps Lady Quinasa of Varshikar. The reasoning remains unknown. Later a letter appearse on the wall and someone called Sonya demands ransom. Search parties start to look for her.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 13th, Alaine reports about a dream which helped her to regain some of her lost memories.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 17th, a halfling finds Quinasa tied to a tree. He tells the search parties and leads them there. The kidnappers seem to have left the island.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 18th, Samantha Meryadeles finds refuge in the castle of the Grey Rose after Aragon ben Galawan intercedes on her behalf.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 20th, Ceigan Ibatha announces that all dwarves could donate their beards to the Prancing Megenta Troll of Madness, to knit old socks out of them.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 20th, A group of drow attack the town. They were defeated. </p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 20th, someone publishes false accusations against Silverbrand in the name of Lennier. It is soon known that they are forgeries. </p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 21st, Lennier complains about the bad behaviour of the guests who entered to barter with Sam in the castle </p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 23th, Erart Ridoc offers lessons in the art of carpentry.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 25th, the town guard invites all to a festival of friendship and comradship.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 26th, a meteor falls to Gobaith and soon after an old man is found near the crash site. After being fed, the man began to grow into a horrific creature, which even attacked and ate a nearby elf. After Aragon used holy water on the beast, it fled into the Southern Woods. There were no sightings afterwards, except for some reports that the monster had been eating the trolls and causing a large mess.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 26th, Faladron Funrir and Marie Tolong announce their engagement. </p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 27th, Cyrus founds the orc clan "Deathscares". It doesn't exist for a long time.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 27th, someone warns everyone about the two orc brother Cyrus and Grutar who call themselves Deathscares and terrorise the island. </p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 27th, Jeremy, leader of the VMA, announces that he recovered from his illness and is now accepting students again.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 28th, someone founds the mysterious group "The Collective" which has the goal to expel the town guard and the Grey Rose from Tolls Bane to establish an own form of government. </p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 28th, Kaja Wolfhagen calls on all orcs to get aware of their pride and to gather under Moshran. He gets into a fight with Cyrus of the Deathscares.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 28th,Lady Arynne searches for the missing Thalodos in the bloodscull territory.</p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 28th, Aragon ben Galwan curses Cyrus of the bloodskulls due to blasphemy. Cyrus turns into a pig afterwards. Only through a prayer a few days later is the curse expelled. </p>
<p>In the year five of the new era on may the 31st, Kaja Wolfhagen, former shaman of the bloodskulls, is slain by the blade of Cyrus. </p>


